The '''New Directors' Showcase''', started in 1991, is one of the award categories at the [[Cannes Lions International Festival of Creativity]].<ref>{{cite web|url= http://saatchi.com/en-us/new-directors-showcase/new-directors-showcase-years/|title= New Directors' Showcase|publisher= Saatchi & Saatchi|accessdate=18 November 2017}}</ref>

It is meant to unearth new directorial talent and is organised by [[Saatchi & Saatchi]].

