'''Nicolas Lehotzky''' is a [[Switzerland|Swiss]] entrepreneur.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.gizmag.com/caterpillar-sram-and-brembo-brands-interpreted-as-watches/9623/|title=Caterpillar, SRAM and Brembo brands interpreted as watches|date=July 12, 2008|work=Gizmag|accessdate=20 March 2012}}</ref> Lehotzky came to international attention in 2008 for presenting a line of [[wristwatch]]es stylized to resemble [[Caterpillar Inc.|Caterpillar]] machinery, [[bicycle]] parts and automotive components.

